name: The Apollos Project Image Preview
description:
Duplicate our Image Preview Template to quickly test how different images display in all of the various card components throughout our UI Kit. This way your creative team can make sure their work looks great in the app.

ABOUT THE APOLLOS PROJECT

Join a community of churches working together to bring people closer to God and advance the Kingdom through technology.
